Microsoft Azure is a comprehensive, secure cloud computing platform offering 200+ services, including AI, compute, storage, and networking. It enables building, scaling, and managing applications via data centers, supporting hybrid environments and specializing in AI infrastructure. Azure operates on a pay-as-you-go model, favoring enterprise-grade reliability. 
