Key Aspects of Azure
Core Services: Offers IaaS (Virtual Machines), PaaS (App Services), and Serverless (Functions) for building apps.
AI and Machine Learning: Serves as the exclusive cloud provider for OpenAI, with infrastructure for AI workloads using NVIDIA and AMD silicon.
Databases & Analytics: Provides SQL and NoSQL managed databases (Azure SQL, Cosmos DB) and analytics engines.
Hybrid & Multi-Cloud: Extends services to on-premises, edge, and other clouds via Azure Arc.
Security & Compliance: Offers multi-layered security across data centers, specializing in data privacy.
Global Reach: Features more regions than any other cloud provider. 
